snippet: Fast-rising Austrian Dominic Thiem out-muscled teenager Alexander Zverev 6-7(4) 6-3 6-3 6-3 to reach his first grand-slam fourth round at the French Open on Saturday....
lead_paragraph: Fast-rising Austrian Dominic Thiem out-muscled teenager Alexander Zverev 6-7(4) 6-3 6-3 6-3 to reach his first grand-slam fourth round at the French Open on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Thiem Overpowers Zverev in Clash of Young Guns
